{"tid":1825980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：中國已承諾採取行動打擊盜版及冒牌貨品","createTime":"2020-01-15T18:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T06:17:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":168,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"f7fa79f4a9c2b10d7d421526aa999f70938dfff6","tid":1825980,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1503018_1_20200116014827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1503018_1_20200116014827.jpg&h=d8a05596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美兩國舉行首階段貿易協議簽署儀式。美國總統特朗普聯同副總統彭斯、財長努欽及貿易代表萊特希澤，與中國副總理劉鶴出席儀式。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普形容首階段協議是非常好的協議，內容包括對知識產權有強而有力的保護，而中國已承諾採取行動，打擊盜版及冒牌貨品。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普指出，貿易協議完全可執行，對貨幣貶值，有一些非常嚴格的限制，有信心美國農民能夠滿足中國對農產品需求的增長。特朗普說，首階段協議簽署之後，將致力第二階段協議的談判，又提到將於不久將來，到訪中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503018-20200116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503018-20200116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=5fd81047\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503018-20200116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7b554ca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503018-20200116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ac85566f0266d47b57ccbebd050a4105b625f66b","tid":1825980,"uid":34065,"like":219,"dislike":2,"score":217,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:35:12.000Z","msg":"唔會有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔抄野 同自斷四肢一樣 無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fdeaae7f5e760a1aaa4312dd867059b145d481","tid":1825980,"uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:41:35.000Z","msg":"Article 1.9 gets at one of the most 