ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7fa79f4a9c2b10d7d421526aa999f70938dfff6","tid":1825980,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1503018_1_20200116014827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1503018_1_20200116014827.jpg&h=d8a05596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美兩國舉行首階段貿易協議簽署儀式。美國總統特朗普聯同副總統彭斯、財長努欽及貿易代表萊特希澤，與中國副總理劉鶴出席儀式。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普形容首階段協議是非常好的協議，內容包括對知識產權有強而有力的保護，而中國已承諾採取行動，打擊盜版及冒牌貨品。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普指出，貿易協議完全可執行，對貨幣貶值，有一些非常嚴格的限制，有信心美國農民能夠滿足中國對農產品需求的增長。特朗普說，首階段協議簽署之後，將致力第二階段協議的談判，又提到將於不久將來，到訪中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503018-20200116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503018-20200116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=5fd81047\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503018-20200116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7b554ca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503018-20200116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:37:05.000Z","msg":"不知所謂的承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1379cf6ca5044b2433189e24d5794f3b59d365d3","tid":1825980,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"你咁即係叫佢執柒淘寶<br />\n邊有可能"},{"pid":"df3c7ae5b6ac5a4ba9ab642f53058aa15c44523d","tid":1825980,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"咁成個淘寶係咪摺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd549c16d4f7a806247f917ed0bd6fe6cb76eaf","tid":1825980,"uid":21678,"lik